A little framework for AJAX-based web applications specifically written for developers 
who like to keep it small and know scala, javascript, html and css well.

Mainly consists of
a) a bidirectional message channel between browser and server
b) a templating mechanism for DOM fragments

To build this code, get and install SBT from 
	https://github.com/harrah/xsbt

Get and install these library/libraries before building:
	https://github.com/ritschwumm/scutil
	https://github.com/ritschwumm/scjson
	https://github.com/ritschwumm/scwebapp

Use these commands to build:
	git clone git@github.com:ritschwumm/rumms.git
	cd rumms
	sbt publish-local
